TRANSLATE

@include.the.translate.command.long

USAGE: spx translate [...]

  CONNECTION                      (see: spx help translate connection)
    --key KEY                     (see: spx help translate key)
    --region REGION               (see: spx help translate region)

  LANGUAGE                        (see: spx help translate language)
    --source LANGUAGE
    --target LANGUAGE

  INPUT                           (see: spx help translate input)
    --microphone                  (see: spx help translate microphone)
    --file FILE                   (see: spx help translate file)
    --files PATTERN               (see: spx help translate files)
    --files @FILELIST.txt         (see: spx help translate files)
    --format FORMAT               (see: spx help translate format)

  TRANSLATION
    --once[+]                     (see: spx help translate once)
    --continuous                  (see: spx help translate continuous)
    --keyword FILENAME            (see: spx help translate keyword)

  ADVANCED
    --log FILENAME                (see: spx help translate log)
    --proxy HOSTNAME              (see: spx help translate proxy)
    --phrases @PHRASES.txt        (see: spx help translate phrases)
    --foreach in @ITEMS.txt       (see: spx help translate foreach)
    --threads NUMBER              (see: spx help translate threads)

SEE ALSO

  spx help setup
  spx help translate advanced
  spx help translate examples
  spx help find topics translate